Interface ITupR

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IColor3R, IColor4R, IHDRColor3R, IHDRColor4R, ILDRColor3R, ILDRColor4R, ITup2dR, ITup2fR, ITup3dR, ITup3fR, ITup4dR, ITup4fR, ITupdR, ITupfR
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ITupR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an n-dimensional tuple. It is used for crossbreeding between the different tuple types e.g. float tuple and double tuple.

    • Method Summary

      double getUni(int index)
